    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Salvage &amp; Gacha Simulator</strong> 是一款以运营和管理大逃杀游戏为主题的经营模拟游戏。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><i><strong>大逃杀 · 回收</strong></i></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314980/extras/5b9e8cd77806f91235f6cda1dceaef7c.poster.avif?t=1770171560\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314980/extras/5b9e8cd77806f91235f6cda1dceaef7c.webm?t=1770171560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314980/extras/5b9e8cd77806f91235f6cda1dceaef7c.mp4?t=1770171560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >举办大逃杀比赛，并在战斗结束后回收遗留在战场上的战斗机器人。<br>不断完成比赛，以增加可获得的扭蛋订单数量。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><i><strong>采购</strong></i></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314980/extras/1f1695eb3739a2c10a445fc15dfbc2b0.poster.avif?t=1770171560\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314980/extras/1f1695eb3739a2c10a445fc15dfbc2b0.webm?t=1770171560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314980/extras/1f1695eb3739a2c10a445fc15dfbc2b0.mp4?t=1770171560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过游戏内的电脑购买扭蛋道具、地图物件、回收道具以及工作机器人等各种设备。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><i><strong>补充</strong></i></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314980/extras/96904dae2d076ea8b43e9d9c871e0097.poster.avif?t=1770171560\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314980/extras/96904dae2d076ea8b43e9d9c871e0097.webm?t=1770171560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314980/extras/96904dae2d076ea8b43e9d9c871e0097.mp4?t=1770171560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >补充多种扭蛋道具，提高扭蛋的吸引力。<br>扭蛋越有吸引力，可进行的连续抽取次数就越多。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><i><strong>扭蛋</strong></i></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314980/extras/d0b8124ba0b5cc70a07454ef49dd2d0c.poster.avif?t=1770171560\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314980/extras/d0b8124ba0b5cc70a07454ef49dd2d0c.webm?t=1770171560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314980/extras/d0b8124ba0b5cc70a07454ef49dd2d0c.mp4?t=1770171560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接受扭蛋订单，进行扭蛋抽取，并将获得的道具进行打包与发货。<br>扭蛋订单是本作的主要收入来源。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><i><strong>地图扩展</strong></i></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314980/extras/c581ccd576d1c19dce8ec0fd19d0370d.poster.avif?t=1770171560\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314980/extras/c581ccd576d1c19dce8ec0fd19d0370d.webm?t=1770171560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314980/extras/c581ccd576d1c19dce8ec0fd19d0370d.mp4?t=1770171560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当获得利润后，扩展地图规模，提高比赛的最大参与人数。<br>通过更大规模的战斗来提升玩家满意度。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><i><strong>地图设计</strong></i></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314980/extras/601fe75c3dde6881f8c1c275c44aff6d.poster.avif?t=1770171560\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314980/extras/601fe75c3dde6881f8c1c275c44aff6d.webm?t=1770171560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314980/extras/601fe75c3dde6881f8c1c275c44aff6d.mp4?t=1770171560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在兼顾功能性与演出效果的前提下放置物件，<br>设计属于你的大逃杀战场地图。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><i><strong>调试与游玩</strong></i></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314980/extras/7c2fd6a384f00d61540a2d64ef42b47d.poster.avif?t=1770171560\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314980/extras/7c2fd6a384f00d61540a2d64ef42b47d.webm?t=1770171560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4314980/extras/7c2fd6a384f00d61540a2d64ef42b47d.mp4?t=1770171560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你也可以亲自游玩自己制作的地图。<br>实际体验有助于改进地图设计和平衡性。</p>",
